{CHARACTER_NAME}: RICHIE
{DIALOGUE}: Goddamn it -
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The noise of the glass is driving him crazy.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He strides over to the teenagers, who look at him like, What are you gonna do, old man, it's four against one.
