{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRANK
{DIALOGUE}: A hundred kilos.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nate blinks like there's something in his eye ...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 55 EXT. BANGKOK - STREET VENDER - DAY
