{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Before they can look any closer, he's put in the ambulance.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As it pulls out, siren wailing, Richie leads Rivera safely away -
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: A60 EXT. ALLEY NEAR STEPHEN CRANE PROJECTS - MORNING
