{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 60 - 69 OMIT 60 - 69 OMIT
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 70 EXT. ARMY BASE, NEW JERSEY - DUSK
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Silence.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Marshland.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A beat-up Chevy parked alongside a perimeter fence.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frank waits by the car as a military Jeep with its lights out comes across a firing range.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It slows, stops.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In it, the silhouettes of three servicemen, black, armed with M-16's.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Silence again, before:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARMY CAPTAIN
{DIALOGUE}: Open the trunk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frank does it, then stands aside as the other servicemen drag four large taped-up duffel bags from the Jeep to his car, lift them into his trunk and slam it shut.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 71 INT. FRANK'S APARTMENT - LATER - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The duffel bags, still closed, on a table.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frank regards them, nursing a drink, putting off the moment of discovery that he has perhaps spent his life's savings on nothing.
{META_DATA}: (CONT)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 31.
{META_DATA}: 71 CONTINUED:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The German shepherd watches as Frank removes the tape from one of the bags.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He pulls it open - has almost no reaction - except to breathe again - then opens the next, and the next.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And we see: Several brick-like packages of No. 4 heroin wrapped in paper marked with Chinese writing, stamped with a label: two lions on their hind legs, paws on a globe, and, in English: DOUBLE UOGLOBE BRAND 100%.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: A72 INT. FRANK'S APARTMENT - LATER - DAWN
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The duffel bags are elsewhere.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The only evidence of any drugs is the small amount Frank has given a chemist - who looks like a Harvard student - to test.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It responds instantly.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The young man looks at Frank.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHEMIST
{DIALOGUE}: Typically what I see is 25 to 45 percent pure.
{DIALOGUE}: I've never seen anything like this.
{DIALOGUE}: No alkaloids, no adulterants, no dilutents.
{DIALOGUE}: It's a hundred percent.
{DIALOGUE}: May I?
