{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRANK
{DIALOGUE}: Take it with you.
{DIALOGUE}: I don't want to have to call the coroner.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The chemist gathers his things to leave, offering a last piece of advice -
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHEMIST
