{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 74 EXT. HOUSE - TEANECK, NEW JERSEY - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frank and the dog in the back yard of a suburban house.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His neighbors - those he can see - are white.
