{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 141 INT. NARCOTICS SQUAD HQ - NEWARK - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jones tapes a tape recorder the size of a pack of cigarettes to Richie's bare chest.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 142 INT. GAS STATION GARAGE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Undercover in a wise guy's cashmere sweater and slacks, Richie watches the mechanic count the $10,000 he's given him.
