{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 62.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 156 EXT/INT. TONY ZACA'S BACKYARD & POOL HOUSE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Barbecue after their Sunday softball game.
