{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANA
{DIALOGUE}: Come on.
{DIALOGUE}: You look great.
{META_DATA}: (no one else emerges)
{DIALOGUE}: You want to miss the fight?
{DIALOGUE}: Come on.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Finally, a patent leather shoe pokes out, sets down on the curb.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then its mate beside it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The shoes step away from the limo and -
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 167 INT. MADISON SQUARE GARDEN - NIGHT
