{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: C265 INT. FRANK'S PENTHOUSE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A large TV shows chaotic scenes in Saigon.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The US is pulling out of Vietnam.
