{DIALOGUE}: Your success is who took a shot at you.
{DIALOGUE}: How you gonna kill it?
{DIALOGUE}: By being unsuccessful?
{DIALOGUE}: You can be successful and have enemies, or unsuccessful and have friends.
{DIALOGUE}: It's the choice we make.
