{DIALOGUE}: They're lettered, A, B, C, D -
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JIMMY
{DIALOGUE}: I'm just telling you what I heard -
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ABRUZZO
{DIALOGUE}: Then you heard wrong!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jimmy shies back a step in case Abruzzo takes a swing.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SPEARMAN
