{CHARACTER_NAME}: RICHIE
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, you'd know, sitting here, having never been on the (street) -
{CHARACTER_NAME}: US ATTORNEY
{DIALOGUE}: Lou, get this fucking kike out of here -
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Richie goes for him and lands several punches before Toback and the others can pull him off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 299 OMIT 299 OMIT
